## Completed Work This Session

### Project: sluice — All 5 phases (Tasks #864-868)
TypeScript drop-in replacement for bottleneck (~4.4M weekly npm downloads). Zero runtime dependencies, Node.js 18+, ESM+CJS dual build.

Core: Sluice class with maxConcurrent, minTime, reservoir (refresh/increase/maximum), priority queue (10 levels, weight), penalty/reward, job expiration, wrap(), chain(), stop/disconnect, updateSettings. Strategy enum (LEAK, OVERFLOW, BLOCK). All lifecycle events (received, queued, scheduled, executing, done, failed, dropped, depleted, empty, idle, error).

Group class: keyed limiter factory with idle cleanup, created event.

Redis clustering: RedisConnection with ioredis support, Lua scripts for atomic check/done/reservoir/heartbeat/init, dead instance detection, Redis 7.x compatible.

Compat layer (`sluice/compat/bottleneck`): Bottleneck class, Strategy, Group, DEFAULT_PRIORITY. MIGRATION.md.

119 tests across 7 test files. 5 commits pushed to agentine/sluice. CI green on Node 20+22. MIT license.

